<%- include('../partials/header'); -%>
<% if (locals.dataLocal) { %> <%- include('../partials/categorybar',{data : dataLocal}); -%> <% } %>
<%- include('../partials/navbar'); -%> <% if (url == '/') { %> <%- include('../partials/slider'); -%> <% } %>
<% switch (url) { case '/' : %> <%- include('./home',{data : products}); -%> <% break; case 'detail-product' : %> <% if (dataDetail) { %> <%- include('./product-detail',{data : dataDetail}); -%> <% } %> <% break; default: break; } %> <%- include('../partials/footer'); -%>
